front.title: •R2-D2 (Artoo-Detoo) (V)
front.gametext: While aboard a starfighter, adds 2 to power, maneuver, and hyperspeed. While with a Scomp link, adds one [Light Side] icon here. Immune to Fire Extinguisher and Restraining Bolt.
front.lore: Feisty. Loyal. Heroic. Insecure. Rebel spy. Excels at trouble. Incorrigible counterpart of a mindless philosopher. Has picked up a slight flutter. A bit eccentric.
